title: Rams, Patriots problems with Brady Quinn (Football 12/18)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn to break down the Bears ascension to Kings of the North (1:00), Vance Joseph's big blunder (11:00), what's wrong with the Rams (13:45), Brady's incredible experience with a Raiders fan during his rookie year (16:30), concern about the Chiefs (23:00), the Eagles big comeback (25:30), the Patriots problems (30:00) and the Saints-Panthers Monday night matchup.
